---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import hero from "../../assets/hero.png";
---

<section class="bg-[#F5F7F7] pt-1.5 pb-6 md:py-12.5 max-md:px-5">
  <div class="container mx-auto">
    <div class="swiper">
      <div class="swiper-wrapper">
        <div class="swiper-slide">
          <div
            class="grid items-center grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 max-md:gap-2.5"
          >
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-1.5 md:gap-7.5 max-md:order-2">
              <h2 class="text-sm font-bold tracking-wider md:text-2xl">
                Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting
                industry
              </h2>
              <div
                class="text-xs md:text-sm font-light tracking-wider text-[#363131]"
              >
                Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting
                industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry's standard dummy
                text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley
                of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book. It has
                survived not only five centuries, but also the leap into
                electronic typesetting, remaining essentially unchanged.
              </div>
              <div>
                <a
                  href="#"
                  class="text-[#346E65] border border-[#346E65] rounded-md py-3 md:py-5 px-14 md:px-25 inline-block text-sm md:text-xl font-medium tracking-wider hover:bg-[#346E65]/10 duration-300"
                >
                  Ətraflı
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mx-auto">
              <Image src={hero} alt="hero" loading="eager" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="swiper-pagination flex items-center justify-center gap-0.5">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<script>
  import Swiper from "swiper";
  import { Pagination } from "swiper/modules";

  const swiper = new Swiper(".swiper", {
    modules: [Pagination],
    loop: true,
    pagination: {
      el: ".swiper-pagination",
      clickable: true,
    },
  });
</script>
